---
title: "US45 — Create / manage expert profile"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpsertExpertProfile
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertProfile
  A->>B: edit bio, credentials, photo
  B->>C: save(profile)
  C->>E: apply edits, persist
  E-->>C: updated
  C-->>B: saved
  B-->>A: public profile updated
  note over E: persisted via SupabaseGateway
